Enjoy a Luxury Experience

CJ Pallazzio Luxury is housed in a stunning building that features a contemporary design with a touch of classic elegance. The interior design is stylish and sophisticated, featuring high-quality materials and luxurious finishes.

The hotel offers 53 spacious and well-appointed guest rooms, including executive and deluxe rooms, and suites. The rooms are tastefully decorated with modern furnishings and feature premium bedding, flat-screen TVs, minibars, and high-speed internet access.

Extra Services

CJ Pallazzio Luxury offers 24-hour room service, allowing guests to order food and beverages to their rooms at any time of the day or night. The menu includes a range of Indian and international dishes, snacks, and beverages.

The hotel's exceptional service, combined with its luxurious amenities and elegant design, makes it an ideal choice for both business and leisure travelers.

Our Services
Hotel Facilities
Pick Up & Drop

The hotel offers airport transfer services to its guests, making it easy and convenient to get to and from the airport.

Parking Space

The hotel has a dedicated concierge team that can help guests with their travel arrangements, including transportation, sightseeing tours.

Room Service

CJ Pallazzio Luxury offers 24-hour room service, allowing guests to order food and beverages to their rooms at any time of the day or night.

Swimming Pool

The hotel's swimming pool is a luxurious outdoor pool, located on the rooftop of the hotel, offering stunning views of the city skyline.

Fibre Internet

The hotel provides complimentary Wi-Fi access to its guests, allowing them to stay connected and productive during their stay.

Breakfast

The breakfast menu includes a variety of dishes, including Indian and continental options, such as eggs, bread, pancakes, waffles, cereals.

Discover

The Restaurant

The menu features a variety of vegetarian and non-vegetarian options, with a focus on traditional Gujarati cuisine. Some of the popular dishes on the menu include Dal Makhani, Butter Chicken, Paneer Tikka, and Tandoori Chicken. The restaurant also offers a range of Chinese and Continental dishes, such as noodles, fried rice, pasta, and burgers.

Experiences

Spa Center

CJ Pallazzio Luxury has a luxurious spa that offers a range of treatments, including massages, facials, and body treatments. The spa also features a steam room, a sauna, and a Jacuzzi.

Learn More
Modern

Fitness Center

The hotel has a well-equipped fitness center, with modern cardio and strength training equipment. The fitness center is open 24 hours a day, allowing guests to exercise at their convenience.

Experiences

The Health Club & Pool

CJ Pallazzio Luxury offers a range of health and fitness facilities to cater to the needs of its guests. The hotel's luxurious pool, state-of-the-art fitness center, and health and wellness services make it an ideal destination for guests looking to stay active and healthy while enjoying a comfortable and relaxing stay.

About Hotel

CJ Pallazzio is a "Business Class Luxury" hotel offering comfort stay for it's guests, located at the Salem - Bangalore NH7 – Junction Main Road Circle, fitted with 72 Rooms, including 12 Suites, 4 Conference halls capable of accommodating more than 800 guests.
